contracted, as reduction will proceed assuming all indices are contracted. \
The default option \\!\\(\\*StyleBox[\\\"UseCache->True\\\", \\\"TI\\\"]\\) \
enables a cache that stores previous results for efficient repeated \
computations. The default option \\!\\(\\*StyleBox[\\\"Tabulate->True\\\", \\\
